sentences: Maria Lucia Moreno Lozañes (Manila, December 13, 1976), better known by her stage name MaLoY, is a Spanish Filipino singer.
She was the second female singer of the German Eurodance act Captain Jack from 1998 until 2001.
She was the second female singer of the German Eurodance act Captain Jack from 1998 until 2001.
